Second,  in his newest post, he states that you have to be 46+ to get &quot;the last couple books&quot;, yet his post before that one said he had found both book 5 and 6 (so all books but the 7th), and looking for the 7th.  but if you check his level at the bottom of the post, you see he was only lvl 43.<BR>
<BR>
Third, before the paineel patch went in, the Oracle said he was only interested in 1 book, not the other 6.  But that may be a clue that you have to get them in order, *however* after the paineel patch the oracle is now looking for the book of scale, and describes what you need to do to finish it.  Which would make getting the books in order thing pointless.  I Believe the oracle is merely a placeholder for many quests, and as a new patch goes up, he seeks another book.<BR>
<BR>
Ok now, to toal, if your *not* lying, and you said its not completable until the runes of kunark come out, tell us the location of the 2nd or 3rd book. Otherwise i will have to consider this quest a dead end.<BR>
